item.title: Project-Blackout Development Team
item.dc:creator: @ezzi ezzi
item.description:
@ezzi wrote:

[center]Admin ? or mod?
Name/Ingame Name:
Joseph/Ezzi

Age:
15

Country/Timezone:
US California Time( I dont know time zones…)

In-game Name(s):
ezzi

Average Activity Time Per Day:
2-3 hours

Position Applying for:
Moderator, admin, or a developer

Previous Experience:
I have programmed about 3 servers, helped others out, I have been staff on various servers( Mainly Moderator) I am familiar with the way the base has been written and I know my way around it from programming and just testing the source. And I am pretty good with advertising. I have also pointed out some of npc glitches and given the Id’s to fix nothing big just thought I’d say

Reason you are applying:
Not for power or to look cool, but to help this server grow because I’m almost 100% sure this could be a big server.

What will you do if chosen to be a moderator:
Same thing I am doing now, playing by the rules, helping out others, advertising, giving Ideas. You know, what any mod would do, unless your the kind of “Power Hungry” mod which I am not.

About Yourself:
I have some knowledge in java, html, c++, and I am pretty good with photoshop and coming up with some Ideas.
Extra Information:
Nothing else really… [/center]
